1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 9=

4
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,519
Why is she here?

5
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,839
She's not exactly our friend,

6
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:22,640
but I don't think
she's our enemy either.

7
00:00:25,920 --> 00:00:27,359
You never know.

8
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:29,320
The Wudu Sect is known for its poisons.

9
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:32,000
Don't let her put you under her spell.

10
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:37,920
I can vouch for Peng Dasheng.

11
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:40,359
He trained under the Wuhuduandao Sect,

12
00:00:40,759 --> 00:00:42,759
a respected orthodox sect.

13
00:00:43,119 --> 00:00:44,000
The Holy Maiden?

14
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,000
How can she prove that?

15
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,280
Who is she?
What's her relationship with him?

16
00:00:50,079 --> 00:00:53,679
Ms. Duan,
the Wudu Sect lies deep in Miaojiang.

17
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:56,520
How could you have ties to a junior

18
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,560
from some obscure little sect?

19
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,320
Could there be some mistake?

20
00:01:01,079 --> 00:01:02,880
Are you questioning me?

21
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,840
I wouldn't dare.

22
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,159
Everyone knows that

23
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:08,079
despite your young age,

24
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:10,239
you already command
the Thirty-Six Caves of Miaojiang.

25
00:01:10,599 --> 00:01:12,200
I have nothing but admiration for you.

26
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:15,560
But this concerns the reputation
of the entire martial world.

27
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:19,840
I must ask you to provide solid proof

28
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,239
so there can be no misunderstanding.

29
00:01:21,319 --> 00:01:24,319
My master, Wu Yangzi, told me himself.

30
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,719
Would you question the word

31
00:01:26,719 --> 00:01:28,000
of the Wudu Sect's leader too?

32
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:29,760
I... I wouldn't dare.

33
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:30,760
I wouldn't dare.

34
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:33,599
But

35
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:35,439
Peng Dasheng clearly used

36
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:37,159
Dongyang ninjutsu just now.

37
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,120
There's no denying it.

38
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:41,159
Every elder here saw it.

39
00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:43,439
If we let this slide,

40
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,319
what will become of the rules

41
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:47,079
of the martial world?

42
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,280
Then let's do it

43
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,159
my way. Disqualify him

44
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,879
from this martial tournament.

45
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:56,879
Only then can order be restored

46
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:58,799
to the Central Plains martial world.

47
00:01:58,879 --> 00:02:00,079
That's right.

48
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:03,200
Exactly. He's right.

49
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,200
Ridiculous!

50
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,000
Exactly!

51
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,000
For centuries,

52
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,360
the Wudu Sect was branded heretical

53
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,400
by the Central Plains martial world.

54
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,599
Miaojiang gu arts were condemned
as dark sorcery.

55
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,919
If the Four Grandmasters

56
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,520
hadn't cleared our name ten years ago,

57
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:21,879
Miaojiang arts still wouldn't
be accepted as orthodox.

58
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:25,800
Miaojiang gu arts and Central Plains
martial arts share the same roots.

59
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,639
Dongyang ninjutsu can't compare.

60
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:29,199
Kun Zhongyu,

61
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:32,039
how do you know I used Dongyang ninjutsu

62
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:33,400
and not an orthodox
Central Plains technique?

63
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,960
You won't admit you're wrong until
it's staring you in the face.

64
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,319
Everyone saw you use

65
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,800
Dongyang ninjutsu.

66
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:40,639
Are you saying

67
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:42,240
all the martial arts elders here

68
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,360
are ignorant fools?

69
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:46,400
That all of them combined

70
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:49,080
know less than a nobody like you?

71
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,639
You're the ignorant one.

72
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:53,639
What I used

73
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:56,000
was the Earth Escape Technique
from the Five Elements Evasion Arts.

74
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,000
It uses the earth

75
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,000
to vanish without a trace.

76
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,120
It's the perfect technique
for escaping danger.

77
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,879
R-Ridiculous!

78
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:07,159
I've traveled the martial world
for over a decade,

79
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,680
and I've never heard of any sect

80
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,280
with an Earth Escape Technique.

81
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,199
Stop making things up!

82
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:13,080
Mr. Peng,

83
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:16,759
do the Five Elements Evasion Arts
you mentioned

84
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:19,039
derive from Secret Talismans,

85
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:22,039
a chapter of the Six Secret Teachings
written by Jiang Ziya?

86
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,159
Exactly.

87
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,960
The technique requires
one of the five elements as a medium.

88
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,919
Earth Escape is only
the most basic form.

89
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:30,080
There are also Wood Escape
and Water Escape.

90
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,599
This arena simply suited

91
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,680
Earth Escape best.

92
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,719
That's an ancient secret art

93
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:38,800
lost for centuries!

94
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,719
An ancient secret art?

95
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:43,960
Isn't it just a simple martial trick?

96
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,159
I thought everyone knew it.

97
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,000
Mr. Peng,

98
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,120
where did you learn it?

99
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,400
During his seclusion,

100
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,599
my master studied many fragments
of ancient texts

101
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:54,560
and happened to grasp the essence
of the Five Element Escape Arts.

102
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,039
When I was little,

103
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:56,800
my fellow disciples and I

104
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,639
even used it to play hide-and-seek
in the mountains.

105
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:02,360
Thinking back, I really miss those days.

106
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,919
Such a profound ancient art...

107
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:06,960
and he used it to play hide-and-seek?

108
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,319
What a waste!

109
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,759
Exactly!

110
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:12,439
People have long said

111
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:15,039
that Dongyang ninjutsu came from

112
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:17,160
the Central Plains'
Five Element Escape Arts.

113
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,439
The Dongyang practitioners
only learned the basics,

114
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,560
yet treasured them
like sacred techniques.

115
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,639
Now,

116
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:26,319
I finally know the rumors are true.

117
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:27,800
Mr. Peng's technique

118
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:31,279
is the authentic form
of the Five Element Escape Arts.

119
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:32,399
That's right!

120
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,759
Yeah! Exactly!

121
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,680
It's definitely orthodox.

122
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,720
Yes, completely orthodox.

123
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:37,079
Of course it is.

124
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,399
There's no doubt.

125
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,720
The Holy Maiden was right.

126
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,519
Kun Zhongyu,

127
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,560
what else do you have to say?

128
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,279
I...

129
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,959
I have nothing to say.

130
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,240
Nothing to say?

131
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:58,079
In that case,

132
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,399
I shall announce the winner

133
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:01,639
of this martial tournament.

134
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,839
The winner is...

135
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:07,759
What's going on?

136
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:09,959
It's Mr. Lin.

137
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:11,040
Yeah.

138
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,959
Yes, Mr. Lin is here.

139
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:18,980
(Lin Zhensheng, Master of Huxiao Manor)

140
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:29,879
Father!

141
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:34,319
Father, I've failed you.

142
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,639
I've disgraced Huxiao Manor.

143
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,079
No, I failed you.

144
00:05:38,759 --> 00:05:41,000
I let you suffer such humiliation.

145
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:47,399
Don't worry.
I'll get justice for you today.

146
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,079
Guards!

147
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,680
Kill him!

148
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:58,319
I've long heard that the master
of Huxiao Manor

149
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,279
has a fierce temper.

150
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:01,120
I didn't know he lashed out at everyone
when he lost his temper.

151
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:02,759
- Mr. Murong.
- Mr. Lin.

152
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:03,680
What is this?

153
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:06,360
Today is my daughter's
martial tournament for marriage.

154
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:08,519
You barged into my home

155
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,560
and now intend to kill someone
right in front of me.

156
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:13,920
You're showing me no respect at all.

157
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,199
Please forgive me, Mr. Murong.

158
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:26,399
My son has suffered
a terrible humiliation today.

159
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,680
As his father,

160
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,439
if I don't get justice for him,

161
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,079
who in the martial world

162
00:06:33,399 --> 00:06:37,319
will ever respect Huxiao Manor again?

163
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,759
I'm only here to kill that boy.

164
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:45,120
I mean no disrespect

165
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,639
to our fellow martial artists.

166
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,720
However,

167
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:53,240
if anyone insists on making
an enemy of Huxiao Manor,

168
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:57,000
I won't back down.

169
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:01,720
Mr. Lin, you're right.

170
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,720
Once the sword is drawn,
there's no turning back.

171
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,120
(Song Qingbo, Yizihuijian Sect's Leader)
What happened today

172
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,120
(Song Qingbo, Yizihuijian Sect's Leader)
is a personal dispute

173
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,879
between Mr. Lin and Mr. Peng.

174
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:11,759
So,

175
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:14,920
I advise everyone else
not to get involved.

176
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:17,279
After all,

177
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:20,240
everyone here is a respected elder
of the martial world.

178
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:23,199
There's no need

179
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,160
to ruin old friendships

180
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:26,319
over an unknown junior.

181
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,639
Exactly.

182
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:30,160
So much for the respected elders
of the martial world.

183
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,079
You all look righteous and honorable,

184
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,560
but you're nothing but cowards.

185
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:38,519
You side with Huxiao Manor
simply because it's powerful.

186
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:39,759
You're too afraid
to stand up for what's right

187
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,879
and refuse to take any responsibility.

188
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,920
Aren't you afraid
the younger generation will mock you?

189
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,759
You ignorant girl!

190
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:44,759
What would you know?

191
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:48,680
A match should end
once the winner is clear.

192
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,879
If Peng Dasheng hadn't gone too far,

193
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:52,680
Lin Dun wouldn't be this badly hurt.

194
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,920
Are we supposed to let

195
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,120
such a reckless man

196
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,319
trample the rules

197
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:59,199
of the martial world?

198
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,480
Am I right?

199
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:04,040
This is outrageous!

200
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:04,839
Completely unacceptable!

201
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,519
Exactly!

202
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:06,519
Everyone,

203
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,839
Lin Dun clearly tampered

204
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:10,639
with the weapon earlier

205
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:13,480
and nearly killed
my friend Peng Dasheng.

206
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,959
Dasheng showed mercy.

207
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:17,399
Not only did he spare Lin Dun,
but he also held back.

208
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:19,959
Every elder here saw it clearly.

209
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:22,120
Now you're accusing us
of breaking the rules?

210
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:22,439
You...

211
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,560
How absurd!

212
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,160
Xiao Ziting,

213
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:30,800
you've barely finished your training,

214
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:33,279
yet you dare speak so boldly here?

215
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:36,480
If your father weren't
the master of Nongxiao Pavilion,

216
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:41,080
you'd already be dead at my feet.

217
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,200
Step back now,

218
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:46,120
or I won't go easy on you.

219
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:46,919
Ziting.

220
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,679
Mr. Lin, since you're here for me today,

221
00:08:58,679 --> 00:09:00,480
do you dare fight me to the death?

222
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:04,240
Life or death, this settles our feud.
What do you say?

223
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:11,320
I've roamed the martial world
for over forty years.

224
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:14,879
Nearly a thousand men
have died by my hand.

225
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,399
What makes an unknown junior like you

226
00:09:17,519 --> 00:09:19,720
think you're worthy of facing me?

227
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:22,679
You aren't scared, are you, Mr. Lin?

228
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,879
It's fine if you are.

229
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,679
You can always send

230
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:29,200
those useless lackeys behind you
to die instead.

231
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,320
But after today,

232
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,159
the master of Huxiao Manor

233
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,080
will have a new title,

234
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:38,159
the greatest coward.

235
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,039
How dare you!

236
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,600
If you're so eager to die,

237
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:46,399
I'll grant your wish.

238
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,879
Come on!

239
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,320
Wait.

240
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:53,639
Before we fight, let's make a wager.

241
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:55,559
What kind of wager?

242
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:57,320
If I lose today,

243
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:59,480
my life is yours.

244
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,720
I won't complain.

245
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:02,320
But if you lose,

246
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:07,440
the Lin family
and everyone in Huxiao Manor

247
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,399
must leave Gusu

248
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:12,080
and withdraw from the martial world
for good.

249
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,639
(He's far too calm.)

250
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:25,320
(Does he really have
some hidden ability?)

251
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,480
(If I back down now,)

252
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:30,000
(how could I ever face
the martial world again?)

253
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:31,840
(The honor of the Lin family)

254
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,399
(cannot be ruined by this boy.)

255
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:35,519
Take the bet! Accept it!

256
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:37,240
With that boy's cultivation,

257
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,879
he's no match for Father.

258
00:10:38,879 --> 00:10:40,440
He has no chance of winning.

259
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:43,720
If you're too scared to accept, old man,

260
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,200
my young master won't force you.

261
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:47,200
Just call him "Grandpa" three times.

262
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,039
Dasheng is generous.

263
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:51,320
He might even consider
sparing Huxiao Manor.

264
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,519
You insolent girl!

265
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,919
How dare you insult my father?

266
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,360
Fine! We'll take the bet!

267
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,240
You arrogant fool!

268
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,799
If I win today,

269
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,399
I'll kill you,

270
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,799
and that sharp-tongued girl

271
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:05,080
beside you

272
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,559
will die with you.

273
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:41,240
Lin Zhensheng's mechanical arts
are unmatched in the martial world.

274
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:43,000
His weapon, Soaring Claw,

275
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,159
ranks second
on the martial weapons list.

276
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:47,720
Dasheng may be at a disadvantage.

277
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,799
You've got a few moves, kid.

278
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:22,919
But that little bit of skill

279
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:23,840
won't get you far.

280
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:26,080
A rookie like you

281
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,600
dares to challenge me?

282
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:30,000
You're way out of your league.

283
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,399
So what if I'm inexperienced

284
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,519
and new to the martial world?

285
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:36,360
I still won't bow to a man like you.

286
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,799
What's wrong, kid?

287
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:03,480
No more boasting?

288
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,399
You're bleeding out.

289
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:06,879
Running out of strength?

290
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:09,440
I've got plenty of blood left!

291
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:12,039
Still talking tough
when you're about to die?

292
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,960
Tianji Armor!

293
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,159
Xiaojiu, are you all right?

294
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,919
I'm fine.

295
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,799
The Tianji Armor protected me.

296
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:43,559
No need to worry, girl.

297
00:13:43,679 --> 00:13:46,559
I'll deal with your young master first,

298
00:13:46,639 --> 00:13:48,519
then send you after him.

299
00:13:50,759 --> 00:13:51,559
Ziting,

300
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:54,600
look after Xiaojiu for me.

301
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,840
All right.

302
00:13:56,759 --> 00:13:57,559
Xiaojiu.

303
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,399
Dasheng!

304
00:13:59,399 --> 00:14:00,039
Come on.

305
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,759
Ever since I came to Gusu,

306
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,559
your family has humiliated me

307
00:14:17,559 --> 00:14:19,120
again and again.

308
00:14:19,919 --> 00:14:21,120
I let all of that go.

309
00:14:21,759 --> 00:14:23,679
But today,

310
00:14:23,679 --> 00:14:25,559
you and your son tried to kill me.

311
00:14:25,799 --> 00:14:26,840
You even tried to harm

312
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,240
the people close to me.

313
00:14:28,559 --> 00:14:32,279
That I will not tolerate.

314
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,159
Such a powerful inner force!

315
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,440
With that much power,

316
00:14:47,639 --> 00:14:49,879
even an ordinary fourth-rank fighter
might not match him.

317
00:14:50,879 --> 00:14:52,799
His qi sea was completely empty
yesterday.

318
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:54,799
There wasn't even a trace
of inner force in him.

319
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:56,320
How could he become this powerful

320
00:14:56,519 --> 00:14:58,159
in just one day?

321
00:14:58,679 --> 00:15:00,200
This is unbelievable.

322
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,840
He always pretends to be weak
so his opponents lower their guard.

323
00:15:05,039 --> 00:15:05,840
No surprise there.

324
00:15:10,639 --> 00:15:13,279
(How can his killing intent
be so strong?)

325
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,559
(Was he hiding his true strength
earlier?)

326
00:15:15,679 --> 00:15:19,320
If Heaven won't punish the Lin family,
I will!

327
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:34,279
Break!

328
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:58,759
Miss,

329
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:02,080
you're not falling for him, are you?

330
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,799
Don't be ridiculous.

331
00:16:03,799 --> 00:16:04,679
Mind your business.

332
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:14,100
♪Come on♪

333
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:19,300
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

334
00:16:21,260 --> 00:16:24,220
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

335
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:27,420
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

336
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:30,500
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

337
00:16:30,900 --> 00:16:33,500
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

338
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:36,980
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

339
00:16:37,220 --> 00:16:40,220
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

340
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:43,300
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

341
00:16:43,460 --> 00:16:46,220
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

342
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:50,100
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

343
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:53,140
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

344
00:16:53,180 --> 00:16:58,820
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

345
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:01,260
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

346
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:04,340
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

347
00:17:05,060 --> 00:17:07,460
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

348
00:17:07,580 --> 00:17:11,260
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

349
00:17:11,860 --> 00:17:13,980
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

350
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:17,020
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

351
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:20,460
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

352
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:24,780
♪I am my own king♪

353
00:17:37,860 --> 00:17:39,420
♪I emerge into the world♪

354
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:41,180
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

355
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,540
♪My pride is my trump card♪

356
00:17:42,540 --> 00:17:44,340
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

357
00:17:44,340 --> 00:17:45,740
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

358
00:17:45,740 --> 00:17:47,500
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

359
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:49,020
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

360
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,740
♪I dare to break every rule♪

361
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:52,060
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

362
00:17:52,060 --> 00:17:53,900
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

363
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:55,140
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

364
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:57,380
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

365
00:17:57,380 --> 00:17:58,900
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

366
00:17:58,900 --> 00:18:00,500
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

367
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,100
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

368
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:03,820
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

369
00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:05,540
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

370
00:18:05,540 --> 00:18:06,900
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

371
00:18:06,900 --> 00:18:08,540
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

372
00:18:08,540 --> 00:18:10,020
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

373
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:11,740
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

374
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:13,340
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

375
00:18:13,340 --> 00:18:14,900
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

376
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:19,220
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

377
00:18:19,220 --> 00:18:21,380
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

378
00:18:21,380 --> 00:18:23,980
♪Let me write the legend♪

379
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:31,420
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

380
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:34,740
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

381
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:37,220
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

382
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:41,300
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

383
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:44,260
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

384
00:18:44,380 --> 00:18:46,740
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

385
00:18:46,740 --> 00:18:49,780
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

386
00:18:49,780 --> 00:18:54,820
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
